Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:22.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（店員）いらっしゃいませー\Nごゆっくり ご覧くださーい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:22.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for shopping with us.\NTake your time looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:23.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子(れつこ)）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:27.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ それ かわいいですよねー\Nサイズなかったら出しますよー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:27.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's cute!\NLet me know if you can't find your size.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ 大丈夫でーす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:28.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:32.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We provide service with a smile,\Neven for those just browsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:30.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ひやかしのお客様も―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:32.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔で対応させて\Nいただいておりまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:34.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ご試着したいときは\N言ってくださいねー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:34.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me if you want to try anything on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:36.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）大丈夫でーす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:35.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:38.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごゆっくり ご覧くださーい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:38.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごゆっくり ご覧くださーい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごゆっくり ご覧くださーい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:44.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごゆっくり ご覧くださーい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:44.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:47.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take my time already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:48.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:53.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:26.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:28.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（レジを打つ音）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:33.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（店員）靴下３足セットのみの\Nお買い上げで 1080円になりまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:33.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Your purchase of just a three-pair\Nset of socks comes to 1080 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:35.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ポイントカードお持ちですかー？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:35.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a points card?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:37.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ… いえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:37.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:40.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,With our current promotion,\Nyou'll get double points - a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ただいま ポイント２倍\Nキャンペーン中なので―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お得ですよー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:42.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）えっと… あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:42.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:46.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）めんどくさいな\N次 いつ来るか分かんないしな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:46.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.\NI don't even know when I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お作りしますかー？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to apply for one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:52.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）あの… け… 結構です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:52.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:53.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:53.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:56.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to apply for one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:56.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お作りしますかー？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:00.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ… じゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:00.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,かしこまりましたー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それでは こちらの記入欄に―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:07.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, just fill this out\Nwith your name and email address.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お名前と携帯のメールアドレスを\Nご記入いただいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't need a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:09.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（プー子(こ)）カードいりませーん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:10.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:16.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,行こ 烈子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Retsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プー子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Puko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I work part-time in Japan, for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（プー子）\N半年 日本でバイトして―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お金が たまったら\Nあとの半年は海外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I've saved enough money,\NI spend the rest of the year abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:35.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お金がなくなったら\Nまた日本で半年バイトして海外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:35.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,If I run out of money,\NI come home and do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:39.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,みたいな生活 高校出てから\Nずーっと繰り返しててさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:39.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've been doing\Nsince we got out of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:43.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,へえー そんなことしてたんだ\Nすごいね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:42.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So that's what you've been up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:43.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,すごくないって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,おかげで いまだに\N定職にも就いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:47.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the reason\NI still haven't got a steady job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:50.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも プー子らしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:52.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's so you.\NIt sounds fun. I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:52.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,楽しそうで羨ましい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:53.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子は働いてんだよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a job, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うん 普通にＯＬ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm a regular office lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of work is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:02:59.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,どんな仕事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:01.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,一応 商社
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a trading firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:03.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そこで経理の仕事してる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I do accounting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,すごいじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:09.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子は昔っから\N真面目で堅実だもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But, then, you've always been\Nthe responsible sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\Nっていうか 私って そんな真面目？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:14.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You think I'm responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だって 烈子ってさ―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:20.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,the kind who never taps "I agree"\Nto an app's terms of service
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,携帯アプリの\N長ったらしい利用規約を―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,端から端まで読み尽くすまで―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:23.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,without reading the whole thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,絶対に 同意ボタン\N押さないタイプでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,普通に押すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The type who's already\Nsaving money for retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,この年で老後のために\N貯金してるタイプ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,してないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（プー子）服屋で何も買わずに\N帰るのは悪いような気がして―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the type\Nwho buys three pairs of socks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,because you feel bad for leaving\Nwithout buying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,とりあえず ３足 千円の靴下\N買っちゃうタイプ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:34.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,当たってる…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:34.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら 真面目じゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You are responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:40.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ま… 真面目なのかな…\Nよく分かんないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I might be. I'm not sure, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:41.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,褒めてんのよ\Nそれが烈子の いいとこだし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good thing about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:46.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ただ そこが ちょっと\N心配でもあるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's also something\NI'm a bit worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:47.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（プー子）人生 楽しめてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you enjoying life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何かさ―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,顔 疲れてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You look... pretty wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:02.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（目覚ましの音）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:07.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:08.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,FOR THOSE WHO WANT A JOB CHANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:20.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根(つぼね)）ハアー 忙しい 忙しい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あら？\Nちょっと疲れた顔してるわね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness! You look a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ… まあ… ちょっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. Are you sleeping properly?\NAre you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あらー ちゃんと寝てる？\N食べてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私 ちょっと\Nあなたに―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I've been leaning too hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,甘え過ぎてたかも\Nしれないわね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:38.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:42.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたを信頼して\Nついつい仕事 振っちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:42.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I share my work with you\Nbecause I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:43.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんなさいね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:43.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,坪根さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Tsubone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:49.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私 最近\N健康のためにジョギングしてるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:49.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I've been jogging to stay healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,これが最初のうちは つらくてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:56.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But I kept at it,\Nand it gradually became easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それでも続けてると\Nだんだん楽になってくるの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Muscles build over time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,きっと必要な筋肉が\Nついてくるのね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:04:59.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:04:59.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:02.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根）つまり！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:06.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,you haven't built up the muscles\Nfor your job yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたは まだ仕事の筋肉が\N足りてないってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:06.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ええっ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根）はい！ どんどん頑張って\N筋肉つけちゃって！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:10.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Keep working hard\Nand build up those muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:16.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time to be tired!\NWe're understaffed right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:16.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,疲れてる暇なんて ないわよ！\Nこの時期は人手が足りないの！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）フン！ フン！\N（烈子）あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see someone\Nwho could help over there, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あそこに人手が\N余ってるように見えるんですけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは仕事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:29.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... his job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:36.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あー とっても忙しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:36.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, am I busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あー とっても忙しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, am I busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（小宮(こみや)）トン部長！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Ton,\Nsorry to bother you while you're busy--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お忙しいところ\N申し訳ありませ～ん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今 手が離せん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:46.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お仕事を増やしてしまい\N心苦しいのですが―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It pains me to increase\Nyour workload, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,but could I have a bit of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,少々お時間を\N頂けますでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,是非 見ていただきたいものが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,フン 見せてみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,北茨城(きたいばらき)にあるゴルフ場なんですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a golf course in Northern Ibaraki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:05:59.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）うむ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,with unbeatable prices!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（小宮）値段も手ごろです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:02.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）うむ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,しかも…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,敷地内に温泉施設もあります
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hot spring on the property.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:10.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）うむ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,小宮よ 忙しくなりそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Komiya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,we've got our work cut out for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:17.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,過労で倒れてしまいそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might collapse from overwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:19.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン･小宮）\Nあー とっても忙しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, are we busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あー とっても忙しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, are we busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あー とっても忙しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, are we busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あー とっても忙しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, are we busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning, grant me your vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit my boss's golf club - find your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning, grant me your vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit the flunky's golf club\NFind your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning, grant me your vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit the witch's head as she runs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:57.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:02.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デス烈子の荒い息）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,よし 戻って仕事しよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子(こ)）烈子 どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）えっ？ 何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）うーん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,多分 烈子のおばあちゃんって―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:22.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking, your grandma\Nprobably looks like you do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,こんな顔なんだろうなー\Nって顔してる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:23.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:27.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああっ！ 狭山(さやま)の ばあちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my grandma in Sayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:32.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田(だ)）烈子 まさか あの仕事\N全部 終わらせたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, don't tell me\Nyou finished all that paperwork...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:34.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）うん 根性で終わらせた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I pushed through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:37.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子･ハイ田）\Nおおー 真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）それ 友達にも言われた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what my friend told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私って そんな真面目？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:45.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really that serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？ ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:48.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,真面目で堅実だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:51.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Serious and reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,携帯アプリの\N利用規約を―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:57.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The type who reads an app's\Nterms of service before tapping "I agree".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,端から端まで\N読み尽くすまで―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,同意ボタン\N押さないタイプ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）それ 友達にも言われた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend said that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The type who starts saving early\Nfor old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,この年で老後のために\N貯金してるタイプ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）それも言われた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子･ハイ田）\N服屋で何も買わずに\N帰るのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:14.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The type who buys some socks to avoid\Nleaving without making a purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,悪いような気がして―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,とりあえず３足 千円の\N靴下 買っちゃうタイプ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だから何で分かるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop freaking me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だって 相手に 何か\N期待されると―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:21.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're the type who is desperate\Nto live up to expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:21.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,身を削ってクソ真面目に\N応えちゃうタイプじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:26.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ… なるほど… そうかも…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:30.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The type that self-destructs\Nfrom doing their boss's job for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,会社では その性格が災いして―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,上司に仕事を押しつけられて\N自滅するタイプ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:31.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,小心者で\Nあるがゆえに―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:35.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,A greenhorn robot caught up\Nin corporate expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,企業の思惑に\Nからめ捕られたロボット
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:36.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:40.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,An obedient corporate slave\Nwho waits in line to die from overwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:40.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）過労死を待つ列に\N自分から並ぶ従順な社畜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ブラック企業を\N肥え太らせるための餌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The fodder fattening up\Nsweatshop companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,おい フェネ子\Nそのへんにしとけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Fenneko, I think you should stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:49.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）\Nあっ ごめん 言い過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sorry. I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:52.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）うーん つまり あれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words... Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子は いい子ってことだよ なっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It means Retsuko is a "good girl". Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:56.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だけど\Nずっと いい子でいるのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:59.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But being a "good girl" all the time is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,tiring, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,疲れるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:14.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:20.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Judgment from everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,And you tell me that I'm just a drone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Bending over backwards for the boss-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:27.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Plain vanilla life 'til the moment I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:33.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Team players lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Team players lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ってことなんだよね…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,多分…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）いつも かっこいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,They always look cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Like working women,\Noverflowing with confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,自信に満ちた働く女性って感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私みたいに中途半端じゃ―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:57.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a pushover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,この人たちみたいに\Nキラキラした存在には―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:01.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never shine like those two do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,なれないんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,かといって―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:07.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, I can't wing it\Nlike Puko does, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:07.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プー子みたいに\N自由に生きることもできない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）超ラッキー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美(わしみ)）どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:18.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,さっき擦れ違った子\Nずっと会いたいなって思ってたの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl we just passed -\NI was hoping to see her all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,朝の占いで 黄色が\Nラッキーカラーだって言ってたから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,My fortune this morning said\Nyellow would be my lucky color.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:25.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）よかったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（メールの受信音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:37.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,ARE YOU DONE WITH WORK?\NCAN WE MEET NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,BAR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（プー子）ういーす お疲れー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers! Long day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:42.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）お疲れさま！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:46.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm not really tired.\NNo job and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:46.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,って私は別に疲れてないんだけどさ\N働いてないし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プハー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Retsuko. Down the hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら 烈子も グーッと空けな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）でさ 職場の飲み会で\Nトン部長に お酌させられるでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:57.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,you know how I have to pour drinks\Nfor Director Ton at work parties?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:59.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,で ビールをこうやって注ぐとさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was pouring the beer like this and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,注ぐときは ラベルを\N上に向けるのが礼儀だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to pour\Nwith the bottle label-side up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you even know that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなことも知らねえのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:13.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the problem with young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:13.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,これだから若い女はよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:15.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ それ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:15.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,思うでしょ？\Nほんと意味 分かんない！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? It doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:22.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなオヤジ 昭和の時代に\N絶滅したんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:22.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't old men like that\Ndie off in the '80s?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:25.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うちには まだ いるんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at our office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:31.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Sockets have started to remind me\Nof Director Ton's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:30.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,最近 コンセントプラグ見ても\Nトン部長の顔 思い出しちゃってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ハッハッハッハッ… うける
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）いつか あいつの顔面に\Nバシーッと―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:38.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I want to slap\Na resignation letter right in his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:38.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,退職願を\Nたたきつけてやりたいんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それが私の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,アッハッハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:45.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子って 話すと 面白いよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:45.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really fun to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ ごめん 私ばっか話してるね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:49.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.\NI'm only talking about myself, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now?\NWill you be in Japan for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プー子は これから どうするの？\Nしばらく日本にいる？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（プー子）うーん…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,んっ んん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:00.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,実は今度 日本でビジネス\N始めてみようかなって思ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was thinking I might\Nstart a business here in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ビジネス！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,A business?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ 先輩と一緒にやるんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, me and a friend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何するの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,輸入雑貨屋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,An imported goods store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:17.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）輸入雑貨屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:17.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,An imported goods store!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,海外から商品 買い付けてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring back products from overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:23.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら 私 向こうにも\Nたくさん友達いるし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:23.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got plenty of friends out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:27.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,自分たちのセンスで 何か\N面白いこと できないかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:27.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,With our tastes, I bet\Nwe could do something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何それ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:28.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's super great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,超すてきなんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,やめてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it. It's not that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,別に そんな大したもんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,最高！ 超羨ましい！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It is! I am super jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:40.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ 一緒にやる？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:40.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... You want in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと待って…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:47.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.\NStop. I just got really shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,やめて 今 本当グラッと来た
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんと？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ やろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:53.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）いや～…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,や… やっぱり会社あるし…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got the company...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:57.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:57.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,辞めちゃえば？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（プー子）\N烈子だったら 経理もできるじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, you can do accounting, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:07.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend and I\Nare the happy-go-lucky types,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:05.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それに 私も先輩も―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ちゃらんぽらんな\N性格してるからさ―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:11.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,so someone responsible like you\Nwould make up for what we lack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:11.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,真面目な烈子と足りないところ\N補い合ってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）何それ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:15.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go overseas to make deals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:15.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（プー子）買い付けのときは\N経費で海外も行けちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）何それ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Wanna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（プー子）ねえ 一緒にやろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\N何それ 何それ 何それ 何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:22.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, seriously, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何それ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,ACCOUNTING DEPARTMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:32.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何やってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:39.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うう… 運動です
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:42.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）あっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:47.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\Nエヘヘ… 掃除がてら 朝の運動を…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning and exercising\Nat the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:48.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）フン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,気楽なもんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,運動したいなら\Nメニューを追加してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the perfect exercise for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Polish my clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,俺のクラブも磨いとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,傷つけんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:59.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scratch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あー とっても忙しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, am I busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あー とっても忙しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, am I busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あー とっても忙しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:07.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, am I busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the carefree one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）気楽なもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,This is practice for the near future,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,このフォームが\Nそう遠くない未来―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:16.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,when I smack you in the face\Nwith a resignation letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,退職願をあんたの顔面に―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,たたきつけるための\N練習だとも知らずに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,辞めてやる…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:19.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,辞めてやる…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,this awful job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,こんな会社！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ お願いね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:34.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）バシーッと辞めてやる！\Nワッハッハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:30.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna quit the crap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitle translation: John Haguewood
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:39.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:10.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
